{
  "stem": "18654.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they-- Auntie Anne was very strict and punished-- punished us easily if we didn't do something that she thought was correct.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember one particular incident, I couldn't have been more than nine years old.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had visitors in the house, and I was told to get ready for bed and come down in my dressing gown and say goodnight.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was very embarrassed by this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I wanted to say goodnight before, but she wouldn't allow it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I had to stand in the corner in the kitchen until I said goodnight.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I think I gave in after about an hour [LAUGHS] and came down in my dressing gown and said goodnight.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there were other little incidents that I remember where she-- I don't think she ever hit me, but she just punished us badly, like that, which was-- I-- I wasn't used to that.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was-- I was smacked, but I wasn't stood in-- I didn't stand in corners for ages.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Another time, I was punished because she thought I had taken some sweets without asking.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "For three days she punished me until my sister took pity, because she had taken them, and admitted it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And little things, funny little incidents like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they seemed very old in my eyes, but they probably were ranging from 40 upwards.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm guessing, I-- I don't really know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They looked very old to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I don't think they were as old as I imagined.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister was a very self-contained girl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was very studious, and she spent most of her spare time hiding somewhere reading, away from me because-- so I didn't annoy her.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she-- she was a very-- very self-contained in that respect.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
